\SE\SE[0] Good work. With this, the mission is complete. \SE[0] I
think you did a great job with your movements. \SE[11] Thanks to
Laura's amazing command.

\SE[33]\SM[pop]Don't try to force yourself to praise me...!
\!\SE[51]I'm not that amazing! \.It's embarrassing!

\SE[80]Overprotective, huh... Seriously.... \SE\SE[7]Well...
since the work is done, let's go home. \SE[7]I'll take care of
the report here. Consider it as payment for the rent.

\SE[5]Oh, about the rent... \SE[3]You don't have to worry about
that kind of thing.

\SE[72]Oh, really...? \.In that case, I'll take you up on your
offer and have you write it instead?

\SE[33]W-Wait, that's...! It's just too difficult, and...!!
\SE[92]Maybe you could work for the rent after all...?
